# [[impulsive|Impulsive]] and [[unpredictable]]; [[determined]] by [[chance]], [[impulse]], or [[whim]]
#: ''I almost died in a '''capricious''' winterstorm.''
#: ''Stringent rulers often act '''capriciously'''.''
